Make the Emercoin ID Application:
 - Log in to any Emercoin ID webserver with EMC SSL certificate (such as https://id.emercoin.net)
 - Create the app
 - Use URI as https://YOUR_WORDPRESS_HOSTNAME/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php?action=emcl_emc_login


Plugin installation and configuration:
 - Zip the folder 'emercoin_id' (such as 'zip -r emercoin_id.zip emercoin_id')
 - Log in to the admin dashboard
 - Upload plugin in the Plugin section
 - Activate plugin
 - Go to Settings -> Emercoin ID, and configure them

After that you can see the "Sign in with Emercoin ID" button at the login page.
